narratives.question_text: What knowledge, skills, and insights did you develop by taking this course?
comments: Intro to Portuguese language, grammar, Brazilian culture.
I learned basic Portuguese and built a beginner language skill-set.

narratives.question_text: What are the strengths and weaknesses of this course and how could it be improved?
comments: The course text is a little weak and is a possible point of improvement. Something more current and dynamic would be more effective. I would say the teaching itself is the strong point of the course and also the accessibility.

narratives.question_text: Would you recommend this course to another student? Please explain.
comments: I definitely would recommend it to anyone interested in Portuguese or starting a new language in general. It's a beautiful language, and it was always a pleasure to come to class and learn every day.
